lyrics:
[Verse]
Lost in the darkness, searching for light
Through the vast emptiness, trying to fight
Hopelessness surrounds, pulling me down
In this endless void, I seek to be found

[Chorus]
Among the stars, I'll find my way
Through the galaxies, where dreams can sway
Euphoria ignites, as I break free
From the helplessness of the void, I will see
